---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cloud Identity Summit 2020">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        
        <div class="mb-12">
            <a href="/archive" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                ← Back to Archive
            </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">
            Cloud Identity Summit 2020
        </h1>

        <div class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 space-y-6">
            <p>The first Cloud Identity Summit took place on October 23, 2020. Originally planned as an on-site conference in Koblenz, the event was held as a virtual conference due to the pandemic. Seven sessions were offered in two tracks.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Sessions & Speakers</h2>
            
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Azure AD Sync – backbone of hybrid setup</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Klaus Bierschenk</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Identity Protection: Deep Dive, find what you usually do not see</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Thomas Detzner</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Azure AD B2B: Notes from the field</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Stephan Wälde</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Building a passwordless World</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Stefan van der Wiele</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">How Yubico technical designs FIDO2 authentication</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Jan M. Quack</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Manage identity lifecycle and access control with Azure AD Identity Governance</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Jan Vidar Elven</span>
                </li>
                <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1">AADInternals - Building a hacking tool</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Speaker: Dr. Nestori Syynimaa</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>